Raspberry Pi 5 (naspi) — 192.168.1.234
│
├── Pi-hole
│   ├─ DNS (port 53)
│   ├─ Local DNS Records
│   │   ├─ pihole.home   → 192.168.1.234
│   │   ├─ files.home    → 192.168.1.234
│   │   └─ home.home     → 192.168.1.234
│   └─ Web UI (port 800)
│
├── Caddy (Reverse Proxy)
│   ├─ HTTP :80
│   ├─ Routes by hostname
│   │   ├─ home.home   → Homepage (Docker :3000)
│   │   ├─ pihole.home → Pi-hole UI (:800)
│   │   └─ files.home  → FileBrowser (:8080)
│   └─ (HTTPS disabled for `.home` domains — correct)
│
├── Docker
│   ├─ Homepage container (:3000)
│   ├─ FileBrowser container (:8080)
│   └─ Future containers (media, monitoring, etc.)
│
├── NAS
│   ├─ 4TB USB HDD
│   ├─ Mounted locally on Pi
│   └─ Shared via FileBrowser / future SMB/NFS
│
└── System Services
    ├─ systemd
    ├─ networking
    └─ storage mounts
